Class FCarsRentalSystem

java.lang.Object
FCarsRentalSystem
public class FCarsRentalSystem
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a rental system. Used to create a rental system for the company. All the data of the car rental system is stored in an object of this class. All directly called functions of the software is defined in this class which works with the help of the other helper functions in different classes.
Since:
2020-10-15
Version:
1.0
Author:
Hani Jafer
